# Deploy context

When the task involves **production or Preview environment variables**, **which n8n webhook URL a deploy uses**, **Vercel (or host) configuration**, or **tracing effective URLs from code**:

1. Read **`docs/deploy-context.md`** first.
2. Do not assume secret values exist in the repo; name the variable and point humans to the hosting dashboard for overrides.
3. Derive defaults from **`lib/n8n.ts`** and the relevant API route (`process.env.N8N_*`).
